This is a terminal blog using Python and MongoDB in reference to the guide that can be found in https://www.udemy.com/the-complete-python-web-course-learn-by-building-8-apps/

User can do the following:
1. Create own blog account
2. View blogs from different users
3. Write own blogs and Posts
4. View own blog posts and other's blog posts as well

Please ensure that you have a running MongoDB connection to your localhost before running the program.

Many thanks to Udemy.
